    "Agents Status tracks your Claude Code and Codex CLI sessions through a small background service that needs Python 3. On macOS, install the Command Line Tools by running `xcode-select --install` in Terminal, then restart Super Island." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Agents Status 通过一个需要 Python 3 的小型后台服务跟踪 Claude Code 和 Codex CLI 会话。请在终端运行 `xcode-select --install` 安装命令行工具，然后重新启动 SuperIsland。"
