    "Another process on this Mac is already listening on 127.0.0.1:%lld. A leftover agents-status server from a previous Super Island run is the most common cause. Open Terminal and run `lsof -iTCP:%lld -sTCP:LISTEN` to find it, then quit that process (or reboot) and relaunch Super Island." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Another process on this Mac is already listening on 127.0.0.1:%1$lld. A leftover agents-status server from a previous Super Island run is the most common cause. Open Terminal and run `lsof -iTCP:%2$lld -sTCP:LISTEN` to find it, then quit that process (or reboot) and relaunch Super Island."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此 Mac 上的另一个进程正在监听 127.0.0.1:%lld。通常是上次运行残留的 agents-status 服务。请打开终端并运行 `lsof -iTCP:%lld -sTCP:LISTEN` 查找该进程，退出它（或重新启动电脑）后再启动 SuperIsland。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
